<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2014-03-20</DATELINE><TITLE>Measurement of CD8 and CD4 T Cell Responses in Mouse Lungs</TITLE><BODY>Study of the adaptive immune response to a viral challenge in an animal model often includes analysis of the T cell response. Here we discuss in detail the methods that are used to characterize the CD8 and CD4 T cell response following viral challenge in the lung.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>